column5: We stayed in cabin #7 for the past several years. Nice cabin! Our group size has gotten smaller. We will be in cabin 1. See you in 9 weeks! üòÉ
66 days and the walleye carnage begins!!!! see you then.

I'll be at Fisherman's Cove on Lac Seul from June 27 - July 4. Any other WC readers going to be there that week? It's always good to meet up, so I like to use WC as the something in common excuse to say hello.
We will be up there July 25 - Aug 1 hope to see other WC readers up there!
Carnhzkr I sent you a pm. Thx
